                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">women</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">What are those women doing there? – They are baking
                            bread.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">āš ydīrin hāk in-<hi rend="red">nasāwīn</hi> hāḏīkin ġādi?
